; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the virtual_null_post path where virtual_balance is a long (integer).
; When balanced virtual postings use bare numbers (no commodity),
; the balance is stored as a long. The null posting gets the inverse.

2024/03/01 Virtual Long Balance
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash      $-10.00
    [Budget:Food]     5
    [Budget:Extra]

test reg
24-Mar-01 Virtual Long Balance  Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
                                [Budget:Food]                     5            5
                                [Budget:Extra]                   -5            0
end test
